reviewText: This is a very good DVD. It is a history told by the actual men. And it is good to know what they went through because the history books will not tell you. This is worth getting.
Title: Red Tails: The Real Story Of The Tuskegee Airmen

reviewText: It was a good lead in to the movie that was released recently. it had some facts that were not available in the movie
Title: Red Tails: The Real Story Of The Tuskegee Airmen

reviewText: I was very impressed with the Tuskegee Airmen Story and how bravethe men were and how hard it must of been to prove yourselfto the world that you were just as good as everyone else.Very good story.
summary: Red Tails. The Real Story of the Tuskegee Airmen
Title: Red Tails: The Real Story Of The Tuskegee Airmen

reviewText: I thought this would be more of a movie, but it was a great documentary.Red Tails: The Real Story Of The Tuskegee Airmen

reviewText: Gift for my dad.  He loves anything related to the Tuskegee airmen!  Highly recommend this movie to any history buff!
